      "blocks": {
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>As the golfing world eagerly anticipates the arrival of the Spring/Summer 2025 season, KJUS introduces a collection that seamlessly blends cutting-edge technology with sophisticated design. Available at TRENDYGOLF, this collection is tailored for golfers who demand both performance and style on the course.​</p><p><strong>KJUS: A Legacy of Innovation</strong></p><p>KJUS has long been synonymous with exceptional quality and innovation in sports apparel. Their commitment to pushing boundaries is evident in their latest offerings, designed to enhance the golfer's experience by providing comfort, flexibility, and protection against the elements.​</p>"
          }
        }
      },
