        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The Spring/Summer 2025 lineup showcases KJUS's dedication to performance-driven design. Among the standout pieces are:</p><h3><strong>Regulator Hybrid Jacket</strong></h3><p>The Regulator Hybrid Jacket in Atlanta Blue is a testament to versatility. It features lightweight insulation at the front to retain warmth without adding bulk, while the back and sleeves are crafted from full-stretch fabric, ensuring unrestricted movement—ideal for an active lifestyle. The moisture-wicking interior lining manages perspiration, keeping you dry and comfortable throughout your activities. An ergonomic stand-up collar with a chin guard adds extra warmth and protection from wind and cold. The bonded quilting on the upper half provides a contemporary look with enhanced insulation. This jacket is composed of 78% Polyester and 22% Elastane, with 100% Polyester insulation (KJUS FAST Thermo Core), and comes in a regular fit, designed for layering without restricting movement.​</p>"
          }
        }
      },
