      "blocks": {
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3><strong>Regulator Gilet</strong></h3><p>The Regulator Gilet in Atlanta Blue offers a lightweight layering option that doesn't compromise on warmth. It features insulated bonded quilting on the front for targeted warmth without adding bulk, while the back is crafted from full-stretch fabric to provide maximum flexibility. Ideal for cool days on the course or as a stylish layer for casual outings, it boasts a moisture-wicking interior lining that ensures you stay dry and comfortable. The ergonomic stand-up collar offers additional warmth and protection, making it a practical yet stylish choice for any activity. This gilet is composed of 78% Polyester and 22% Elastane, with 100% Polyester insulation (Eco Synthetic Down + KJUS FAST Thermo Core), and comes in a regular fit, perfect for layering without restricting movement.​</p>"
          }
        }
