      "blocks": {
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3><strong>Shift Half Zip Mid Layer</strong></h3><p>The Shift Half Zip Mid Layer in Alloy combines technical excellence with sleek, minimalist style, ideal for golfers who prioritise performance and elegance on the course. This mid layer is crafted with KJUS's innovative VaporTemp fabric, designed to help regulate body temperature by optimising moisture evaporation, ensuring you remain cool, dry, and comfortable even during vigorous play. The ultra-stretch fabric and Y-Tech cut allow full freedom of movement, letting you swing without restriction. With a stand-up collar and chin guard, it provides added warmth and coverage when the temperature drops, making it a versatile layer for all conditions. This mid layer is composed of 83% Polyamide and 17% Elastane, and comes in a regular fit, designed to provide comfort without bulk.​</p>"
          }
        }
      },
