    "text_5": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3><strong>Hollow Pima Polo</strong></h3><p>The Hollow Pima Polo in White is a premium golf polo that combines timeless style with advanced fabric technology, offering unparalleled comfort and performance. Crafted with Hollow Pima Cotton technology, this polo provides natural thermoregulation, keeping you cool and comfortable even in warm weather. The ultra-soft, breathable fabric wicks moisture away from the skin, ensuring you stay dry throughout your game. With a Y-tech cut for enhanced freedom of movement, this polo is ideal for an unrestricted swing. The self-fabric collar and classic three-button placket add a refined touch, making it a versatile choice both on and off the course. This polo is composed of 92% Cotton and 8% Elastane, and comes in a comfort fit, tailored for ease without restriction.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
