    "text_6": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3><strong>Iver Shorts & Trousers</strong></h3><p>The Iver Shorts in Birch are a sophisticated, high-performance choice for golfers looking for style and functionality in warm-weather wear. These tailored shorts are crafted from lightweight, four-way stretch fabric, providing exceptional comfort and unrestricted movement on the course. The water- and dirt-repellent finish ensures you stay looking sharp, while the breathable material keeps you cool during hot days. Thoughtful details, such as the anti-slide scorecard pocket and silicone grip waistband, add convenience and practicality, making these shorts ideal for both the golf course and casual settings. These shorts are composed of 85% Polyamide and 15% Elastane, and come in a tailored fit, balancing style and functionality.​</p><p></p><p>The Iver Tailored Fit Trousers in Atlanta Blue are the perfect fusion of sophisticated style and high-performance functionality, designed for golfers who value comfort and elegance. Made with lightweight, breathable fabric, these trousers feature four-way stretch for unrestricted movement, allowing you to focus on your game without distraction. The water- and dirt-repellent finish ensures you stay clean and dry, while the tailored fit creates a sleek, modern silhouette that transitions seamlessly from the course to casual wear. With thoughtful details such as an anti-slide scorecard pocket and a silicone grip waistband, the Iver Trousers offer both practicality and style. These trousers are composed of 85% Polyamide and 15% Elastane, and come in a tailored fit, designed for style and functionality.​</p>"
          }
        }
      },
